section.def:
Authority
                (監督) means the authority designated under
                section 4;

Chairman
                (主席) means the chairman appointed under
                section 28(1);

container
                (盛器) includes a box, barrel, drum or other
            receptacle;

incineration
                (焚化) means the combustion of substances and
            articles for the purpose of their thermal destruction;

master
                (船長), in relation to a vessel, includes the
            person for the time being in charge of the vessel;

permit
                (許可證) means a permit issued under this
            Ordinance;

paragraph.content:
analyse or have tested and analysed a substance, article, vessel, aircraft
                    or marine structure that is permitted to be dumped, scuttled or incinerated;
                    and
